    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.課程介紹、老化<br>2.生理學原理與老化機制<br>3.積極老化與全人健康<br>4.身體活動與老化<br>5.老人功能性體適能的概念與評量<br>6.老人心肺適能指導<br>7.高齡相關議題與新聞<br>8.老人肌肉適能指導<br>9.老人柔軟度指導<br>10.老人平衡力指導<br>11.老人高血壓之運動指導<br>12.老人糖尿病之運動指導<br>13.如何指導老人開始運動<br>",
        "en": "1. Course introduction<br>2. Physiological principles and aging mechanisms<br>3. Active aging and whole-person health<br>4. Physical activity and aging<br>5. The concept and assessment of functional fitness of the elderly<br>6. Elderly cardiopulmonary guidance<br>7. Senior issues and news<br>8. Elderly muscular fitness guidance<br>9. Elderly softness guidance<br>10. Elderly balance guidance<br>11. Exercise guidance for the elderly with hypertension<br>12. Exercise guidance for the elderly with diabetes<br>13. How to guide the elderly to start exercising<br>"
